prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, 2D flat illustration style with simple elegant shapes and a clean white background. Centered text in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script says "Happy Birthday, Jordan". The artwork depicts cartoon versions of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo, full-body, in a funny and dynamic scene. Jordan is heroically snowboarding down a giant, perfectly marbled slice of wagyu steak as if it's a snowy mountain. He is mid-turn, kicking up a spray of rice instead of snow. He is wearing his dark t-shirt from the photo along with snowboard gear. Lao Lao is at the bottom of the "steak mountain" with a joyful, cheering expression, wearing her white jacket from the photo. She is holding a pair of giant chopsticks, ready to catch him. The scene is humorously littered with other personal details: sushi rolls like salmon nigiri and tuna maki are scattered around like rocks on the slope, a Chinese takeout box sits open nearby, and floating in the air are minimalist green icons representing lines of code, like "< / >" and "{ }". The overall composition is playful, clean, and full of personal jokes.
